{"tid":766003,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"感情出問題","createTime":"2018-08-03T08:49:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T09:09:57.000Z","uid":151789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dba869c33c16200256f1156a56458bda546943a8","tid":766003,"uid":151789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:49:05.000Z","msg":"手機彈出了一個提示<br />\n「你有1個未解決的問題」<br />\n我輕輕掃走它<br />\n隔天，我的手機有2個未解決的問題<br />\n我朋友問我為甚麼放縱不解決<br />\n我說，<br />\n即使不解決，手機也能照運作。<br />\n他說，<br />\n但你知道問題是不會自己消失的啊<br />\n我有點累了，說，<br />\n手機老了，有很多珍貴的回憶在裏面<br />\n若冒險重新開機，可能有些東西便消失了<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/164737_b4d78016ea93be755e46466b47133e12.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F164737_b4d78016ea93be755e46466b47133e12.png&h=b2ca663d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"029d924c80c69f72e6748c73298fc6f503f3609b","tid":766003,"uid":151789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T09:09:57.000Z","msg":"有時掃走左個提醒，打鋪機，就可能有幾刻忘記左個問題"}]}